Plain-English summary (informational, not the license)

You CAN:
  - Run Pare on your own servers / VPS, for free, forever.
  - Use it for your own business, internally and commercially.
  - Use it to keep the books for your own clients (e.g. an accountant or
    bookkeeper running a client's accounting on Pare).
  - Read, modify, and self-distribute the source, keeping this license.

You CANNOT, without a separate commercial agreement from the Licensor:
  - Sell Pare, or offer it to third parties as a hosted or managed
    service whose value derives substantially from Pare's own
    functionality (i.e. a competing "Pare cloud" / SaaS).
  - Remove or obscure the licensing, copyright, or attribution notices,
    or use the "Pare" or "Bright Interaction" names or logos for a
    fork without permission.
